# transient session/runtime files (but keep committed skills under .claude/skills/)
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.lock

# --- privacy: never commit user photos ---
# The style analysis handles images locally only. Keep every photo out of git so a
# clone-and-run never accidentally uploads someone's pictures via a commit/push.
# (Doc assets, if ever needed, can be force-added with `git add -f`.)
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.gif
*.bmp
*.webp
*.heic
*.heif
*.tif
*.tiff
images/*
!images/README.md
